            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              Not sure what's wrong? Get a complete system analysis with transparent pricing. Fee credited toward repairs.
            </p>
            <span class="text-red-600 font-bold inline-flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
              Book Now
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
